    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clamps used as temporary fasteners during filmmaking, for example to affix gels or diffusion materials to the barn doors of hot lights. The common "clothespins (laundry  fasteners)" may be utilized for this purpose.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
